2. cs.GR (Graphics) - The paper discusses the use of omnidirectional images in virtual reality systems, which is a common topic in graphics research. 
3. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with processing and enhancing multimedia content, specifically omnidirectional images. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes the use of a generative adversarial network for super-resolution, which is a common technique in AI research. 
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the use of adversarial learning and proposes a new loss function, which are common topics in machine learning research.
